72
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:40,190
Projects with positive ROIs will cover the investment required to build the product.

73
00:04:40,190 --> 00:04:44,975
Projects with negative ROIs will not and won't make sense to pursue.

74
00:04:44,975 --> 00:04:49,625
Calculating the payback period allows you to understand how long it'll take

75
